  <summary date="2019-02-06T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Space Resources Institute Act

This bill directs the National Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA) to submit a report on the merits of, and options for, establishing an institute related to space resources in order to advance NASA's objectives for maintaining U.S. preeminence in space.</summary>
